categories: Category:Moffs and Grand Moffs of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: A Moff of the reconstituted Sith Empire owned a personal yacht during the Great Galactic War with the Galactic Republic. In 3668 BBY, the Moff's yacht was stolen by a Republic strike team, who used the yacht to board the dreadnaught that ferried the Sith Lords known as the Dread Masters.
